qas.question: Babson College is what type of institution?
What small private law school is located in Boston?
What was the name of Americas first all female law school?

context: <a0_0>Smaller private schools<a0_0/> include Babson College, Bentley University, Boston Architectural College, Emmanuel College, Fisher College, MGH Institute of Health Professions, Massachusetts College of Pharmacy and Health Sciences, Simmons College, Wellesley College, Wheelock College, Wentworth Institute of Technology, <a1_0><a2_0>New England School of Law<a2_0/><a1_0/> (originally established as America's first all female law school), and Emerson College.
